    "agendaChanges": "Per the minutes and transcript, the Reception (Section 5) was moved to occur before the Annual Board Officer's Rotation (Section 4). The oath of office (Section 3) occurred before the reception, and the Annual Board Officer's Rotation occurred after the reception. This resequencing was noted under Changes to the Agenda (Section 6). The actual order was: Call to Order, Roll Call, Welcome, Oath of Office, Reception, Annual Board Officer's Rotation, Changes to the Agenda, Approval of Agenda, then the remaining items in order.",
